        <div class="col-md-6 text-content">
          <h1>
            Expert Guidance on Documentation Process and Requirements for
            Abroad Study Visa
          </h1>
          <p style="text-align: justify">
            There are requirements and complications one has to prepare prior
            to the lodgment of a visa application. If you are planning to
            travel, then it is best to mark up your calendar for your travel
            dates and Visit us for your Visa application at least 3 months
            beforehand to know your Visa requirements and apply for your visa
            in a timely manner. It is always recommended to arrange the Visa
            lodgment appointment at least 14 days prior to your lodgment. When
            applying for the visa you should bear in mind that you are
            submitting documents with reason for travel and showcase your
            genuine intention to return to your home country. Every country
            shares more or less the same requirements for issuing a visa.
            However, there are slim differences here and there, depending on
            the country you are visiting, documents additional to the main
            identification papers, and your current economic status.<br />
            However, A One Global Consultants ensures the applicants avoid any
            legal issues that may occur in relation to their relocation by
            assisting them in obtaining visas and other related documentation.
            At A One Global Consultants our trained counselors provide free
            visa guidance to all the applicants. We guide our applicants in
            the entire visa process from filling up applications, and
            preparing financial statements to training candidates for mock
            interviews. We have up-to-the-minute information about visa
            requirements for destinations and give individual priority and
            guidance on a case-to-case basis.
          </p>
          <p><strong>Some of the Documents you need are:</strong></p>
          <ol>
            <li>Passport with at least 12 months remaining validity.</li>
            <li>Citizenship documents.</li>
            <li>Reason for Travel.</li>
          </ol>
          <p>&nbsp;</p>
          <p><strong>USA Student visa: </strong></p>
          <p style="text-align: justify">
            USA Student Visa : America also known as THE LAND OF OPPORTUNITY,
            has always been the number one choice of destination for students.
            The cheaper tuition fee with massive scholarships in Universities
            is one of the major factors. Students who want to nail a US Visa
            Interview are recommended to also appear for their SAT or GRE /
            GMAT, this gives students an edge toward their commitment to study
            in America. A One Global Consultants represents more than 60
            prominent Universities. Our Interview Preparation sessions
            conducted are research-based. With Interview Dates being fully
            booked in India at times, Our Delhi office will also assist our
            Indiaese students get their US Visa Interview appointment in
            Delhi. It is adviced to at least start preparations a year ahead
            if the USA is your choice of country for Overseas Education. Major
            Intakes are Jan &amp; September with few Universities having other
            intakes in between.
          </p>
          <p>&nbsp;</p>
          <p><strong>Australian Student visa:</strong></p>
          <p style="text-align: justify">
            You are required to lodge your application for an Australian
            student visa at least 3 Months before the orientation date at your
            institution. An Australian student visa allows you to stay in
            Australia to study full-time in a recognized educational
            institution. In the duration of the Australian student visa
            process, you must have applied for and been accepted to study in a
            registered full-time course at an educational institution in
            Australia. Apart from offering the right Australian student visa
            advice, expert counselors at A One Global Consultants, will also
            review your documents. We represent more than 50 Australian
            Universities and Private Colleges offering Diploma to Masters
            Research Degrees. With our office in Brisbane our students located
            in whichever Australian City are satisfied with our services,
            beginning their Journey as Students from India to their Migration
            Visa later in Australia.
          </p>
          <p>&nbsp;</p>
          <p><strong>UK Student visa: </strong></p>
          <p style="text-align: justify">
            To obtain a UK visa, you must qualify for the Tier 4 points-based
            system. You must have at least 40 points to get a student UK visa.
            Likewise, you will need to have proven sufficient Maintenance
            Funds available to you for your study period in the UK. One
            doesn’t need much financial documentation but must be sure that a
            UK degree is what they are after. We have also successfully
            enrolled many students in UK Universities inside and outside
            London. Most popular degrees are for Masters, where the course
            duration is 1 year. Few master&#8217;s Degrees also provide
            additional duration for internships.
          </p>
          <p>&nbsp;</p>
          <p><strong>Canadian Student visa: </strong></p>
          <p style="text-align: justify">
            Also called a Study Permit, a Canadian visa requires you to submit
            documents that include the unconditional acceptance letter, fee
            receipt, financial documents, scholarship letter if any, medical
            reports, work experience details, and test scores. Our North
            American team of Consultants specializes in Canadian education and
            study permit applications, where we have assisted many students
            enrolling successfully in College Diploma, Bachelor, PG Diploma,
            Masters in more than 20 Canadian Colleges we represent and work
            with.
          </p>
          <p>&nbsp;</p>
          <p>
            <strong
              >Why A One Global Consultants is the Best at Student Visa
              Application:</strong
            >
          </p>
